HEADWORD: Antanagoge
<hw>Ant`an*a*go"ge</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>anti-</ets> + <ets>anagoge</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Rhet.)</fld> <def>A
figure which consists in answering the charge of an adversary, by a
counter charge.</def>⟦br⟧
